# ============================================================================
# DOCUMENTATION STANDARDS
# ============================================================================

## README.md Requirements
- Must contain these keywords naturally: "country picker", "flag selector", "phone number", "country code", "international", "multi-language"
- First paragraph must be under 160 characters (meta description length)
- Include comparison table with competing packages
- Minimum 5 complete code examples
- Add "Use Cases" section with real-world scenarios
- Include troubleshooting section
- Add badges: pub.dev score, likes, popularity, pub points
- Structure: Why Choose > Demo > Installation > Quick Start > Examples > API Reference > Troubleshooting > Contributing

## Code Comments
- All public APIs must have dartdoc comments
- Include @example tags in documentation
- Use keywords naturally: "country selection", "flag display", "dial code"
- Add @see tags linking related methods

Example:
```dart
/// Displays a customizable country picker for Flutter applications.
///
/// Perfect for international phone number inputs, country selection forms,
/// and multi-language applications. Supports 20+ languages with SVG flags.
///
/// Example:
/// ```dart
/// FlagSelector(
///   flagSelectorLanguageCode: 'en',
///   onFlagSelectorCountryChanged: (country) {
///     print(country.name);
///   },
/// )
/// ```
///
/// See also:
/// - [Country] for country data structure
/// - [FlagSelectorMode] for display options
class FlagSelector extends StatefulWidget {
  // ...
}
```

## CHANGELOG.md Rules
- Each entry must be descriptive, not just "bug fixes"
- Use keywords: "improved country search", "added language support", "enhanced flag display"
- Link to issues/PRs
- Format: ## [Version] - Date, ### Added/Changed/Fixed

Example:
```markdown
## [1.2.0] - 2025-01-15

### Added
- Vietnamese language support for country names
- Advanced search by country dial code
- Favorite countries feature for quick access

### Improved
- Country picker performance by 40%
- Flag rendering quality on high-DPI screens

### Fixed
- Country search not working with accented characters (#23)
```

